SUMMARY:Poison Arrow: An Alternative Dance Night
DESCRIPTION:KNRK2 presents Poison Arrow: An Alternative Dance Night \nDJ Gregarious and VJ Disorder distill the best and most danceable 80’s & 90’s New Wave\, Post-Punk\, Brit Pop\, and Alt-Club dance songs. From deep cut favorites to club classics\, join us for a night reminiscent of an era when dance club culture reigned supreme. \nPoison Arrow is based on the authentic alternative club sounds and visuals that came from pioneering dance clubs like Mudd Club\, Danceteria\, & Tier 3 in New York City; Kabuki Club\, DV8\, & The I-Beam in San Francisco; and Blitz Club & Blow Up in London (among others).
URL:https://www.crystalballroompdx.com/events/273756-poison-arrow-an-alternative-dance-night/
CATEGORIES:March
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.crystalballroompdx.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/poisonarrow25-85bD50.jpg
END:VEVENT
