SUMMARY:Chris Webby
DESCRIPTION:Chris Webby is a popular American rapper from Norwalk\, Connecticut\, known for his energetic “frat rap” style\, lyrical skill\, distinctive flow & detailed wordplay. Inspired by artists like Dr. Dre and Eminem\, he gained traction performing at college parties. He built a strong fanbase through free online releases and YouTube\, collaborating with artists like Mac Miller\, Freeway\, and DMX\, and founded his own label\, EightyHD Music. 
